-- Schiavone Beats U.K.’s Robson to Reach Second Round at Wimbledon
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2012-06-26T12:57:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-26/schiavone-beats-u-k-s-robson-to-reach-second-round-at-wimbledon.html
Former French Open champion
Francesca Schiavone defeated Britain’s Laura Robson to reach the
second round of the Wimbledon tennis tournament.  The Italian won 2-6, 6-4, 6-4 over the 18-year-old Robson.
Schiavone, who won at  Roland Garros  in 2010, is making her 48th
consecutive Grand Slam appearance, the longest active streak.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  